<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro-body">
<p local-id=3D"21d080e18041">We recommend you export this letter as a pdf o=
r word document once you are finished.</p>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"3fabe0c29544"></p>
<p local-id=3D"8800761b2a21"><span data-colorid=3D"i6h0w9dl1l">&lt;Type // =
to add a date&gt;</span></p>
<h2 local-id=3D"987a6591cf18" id=3D"EmployeePromotionLetterTemplate-Dear<Em=
ployeename>,"><img class=3D"emoticon emoticon-laugh" data-emoji-id=3D"1f600=
" data-emoji-shortname=3D":grinning:" data-emoji-fallback=3D"\uD83D\uDE00" =
src=3D"17ebb4ac8aef77cec9a0156ecda5283ba9a94904f7721b6bbe79d63a064e890a" wi=
dth=3D"16" height=3D"16" data-emoticon-name=3D"laugh" alt=3D"(big grin)">&n=
bsp;Dear <span data-colorid=3D"tu5hhxr5no">&lt;Employee name&gt;</span>,</h=
2>
<p local-id=3D"d3bcac54803e">Congratulations on your promotion to the posit=
ion of <span data-colorid=3D"jphg26hrx2">&lt;Job title&gt;</span>, effectiv=
e <span data-colorid=3D"rwbtpkbatb">&lt;Type // to add a date&gt;</span>. W=
e appreciate your hard work and commitment to the <span data-colorid=3D"ops=
klr2r1j">&lt;Company name&gt;</span> team for the last <span data-colorid=
=3D"uu1gy2ugaa">&lt;Add number&gt;</span> years.</p>
<p local-id=3D"3924780b1559">The annual salary for this position will be <s=
pan data-colorid=3D"goqa80sxj6">&lt;Salary number&gt;</span> paid on a <spa=
n data-colorid=3D"azosb2gka8">&lt;weekly/biweekly/monthly/annual&gt;</span>=
 basis. You will report directly to <span data-colorid=3D"rxf57c8zpl">&lt;N=
ame of manager, Job title&gt;. &lt;Name of manager&gt;</span> is excited ab=
out your new role and will be reaching out to discuss any new job responsib=
ilities and transition plans.</p>
<p local-id=3D"b6ef5d0cd724">Again, congratulations on the new position. Pl=
ease let me know if you have any questions regarding your compensation and =
benefits package.</p>
<p local-id=3D"702fb873371d">Sincerely,</p>
<p local-id=3D"5af704e1418b"></p>
